	(text "The LRCLK must be equal to the\nsample rate, Fs, and must be\nderived from the supplied\nmaster clock, OMCK, or the\noutput of the PLL.\n\nThe serial bit clock, CX_SCLK,\nmust be synchronously derived\nfrom the master clock and be\nequal to 128x, 64x, 48x or 32x\nFs, depending on the interface\nformat selected and desired\nspeed mode."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 277.876 211.836 0)
		(effects
